---
title: Char Siu Chicken & Veggie Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice & Coriander
description: Sticky and fragrant, it’s char siu chicken, ready in a blink of an eye to satisfy all your stir-fry needs. Fluffy jasmine rice is must to soak up all the rich sticky sauce because we can’t get enough of this char siu stir-fry.
